						               													<description>Put yourself in place of the greatest heroes and commanders of Argentina's history and free this land with honor, wisdom and strategy. Oid Mortales el grito sagrado. LIBERTAD!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;O&amp;iacute;d Mortales is a trivia game with strategy combat in a board. Players will have to manage tokens, playing infantry and artillery cards which will fight in surprise trivia, where be the expert historian is not necessarily good. The tactic board gives an expansion to the game far beyond questions and answers, where movement and intelligent use of resources is important as the battle itself.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player will take the side of the &amp;quot;Patriotas&amp;quot; and the other the &amp;quot;Realista&amp;acute;s&amp;quot; side. During the game the players draw cards and put or move the battalions on the map in relation to the action points (AP) obtained in the die roll.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each team will have 4 commanders that have special fight habilities, one of them will be the Gold Commander.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The dice roll give action points (AP) to the players. The actions cost from 2 AP to 6 AP, depending on the type of action. For example take an artillery card cost 2 AP but an event card cost 6 AP.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When a unit is next to an enemy unit, the player can attack. Each artillery or reinforcement card, wich are used to attack, include an historical trivia. The attacker increase or decrease his AP by answering de question.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player who eliminate the enemy Gold Commander enemy wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
